B.Wl=new A.c("At what time interval post-injury does GFAP typically peak?","20-24 hours")
B.WF=new A.c("How does the peak time of UCH-L1 compare to GFAP?","UCH-L1 peaks earlier (8-12 hours) and clears faster.")
B.Vk=new A.c("Which CT scoring system uniquely incorporates diffuse axonal injury (DAI) into its grading?","Stockholm CT Score")
B.ZX=new A.c("How does the Stockholm CT Score treat midline shift differently than the Marshall or Rotterdam scales?","It uses midline shift as a continuous variable rather than a binary cutoff.")
B.Wx=new A.c("In the Helsinki CT Score, how is an epidural hematoma (EDH) weighted?","It is assigned -3 points (acting as a protective/favorable factor).")
B.RO=new A.c("Which specific brain cistern does the Helsinki CT Score evaluate instead of general 'basal cisterns'?","Suprasellar cistern")
B.YR=new A.c("According to multicenter evaluations, which single CT finding is the strongest predictor of an unfavorable outcome?","Traumatic subarachnoid hemorrhage (tSAH)")
B.UP=new A.c("Between the Marshall, Rotterdam, Stockholm, and Helsinki scores, which has the highest overall prognostic performance (Pseudo-R-squared)?","Stockholm CT Score")
B.a_F=new A.c("What is the main diagnostic advantage of using abbreviated MRI protocols in pediatric TBI?","Avoidance of ionizing radiation exposure")
B.Vq=new A.c("What is the primary barrier to implementing ultra-early MRI in the emergency department setting?","Scanner availability and staffing")
B.MY=new A.c("How does 7T MRI compare to 3T MRI regarding the detection of microhemorrhages?","7T detects significantly more microbleeds than 3T.")
B.N2=new A.c("Which small vascular-related pathology is resolvable at 7T but often unresolvable at 3T?","Cortical microinfarcts (or intracortical microhemorrhages)")
B.Ob=new A.c("What is the current role of AI/Machine Learning in neuroimaging triage?","Flagging urgent scans for immediate physician review")
B.Tn=new A.c("Which FDA-approved PET tracer is used to visualize tau pathology in vivo?","Flortaucipir (AV-1451)")
B.N0=new A.c("What is the pathognomonic Tau PET pattern for Chronic Traumatic Encephalopathy (CTE)?","Uptake at the depths of cortical sulci")
B.Uh=new A.c("How does the amyloid profile typically differ between CTE and Alzheimer's Disease?","CTE is often amyloid-negative, while Alzheimer's is amyloid-positive.")
B.Wr=new A.c("If amyloid is present in a CTE case, what is its typical morphological appearance?","Diffuse plaques (unlike the neuritic plaques of AD)")
B.PE=new A.c("FDG-PET hypometabolism in TBI reflects the signal of which two cell types?","Neurons and glial cells")
B.S4=new A.c("TSPO PET imaging is used as a biomarker for what biological process post-TBI?","Neuroinflammation (microglial and astrocyte activation)")
B.Zz=new A.c("In which TBI phase (acute vs. chronic) is TSPO PET signal typically highest?","Chronic TBI")
B.VO=new A.c("What does the 'Free Water Volume Fraction' in advanced DTI measure?","The extracellular water fraction (separating edema from tissue damage)")
B.U_=new A.c("In the NODDI model, what does the Neurite Density Index (NDI) estimate?","Axonal integrity and density")
B.Ne=new A.c("In the NODDI model, what does the Orientation Dispersion Index (ODI) measure?","Neurite fanning or fiber disorganization")
B.Zn=new A.c("What is the primary advantage of Fixel-Based Analysis (FBA) over standard DTI?","It resolves crossing-fiber ambiguity by analyzing individual fiber populations.")
B.SM=new A.c("Which imaging metric is more sensitive than SWI for detecting microhemorrhages and iron-related damage?","Quantitative Susceptibility Mapping (QSM)")
B.Nu=new A.c("In CT Perfusion (CTP), what brainstem blood flow threshold suggests a non-survivable TBI?","CBF < 10 mL/100g/min")
B.VT=new A.c("In CT Perfusion (CTP), what brainstem blood volume threshold suggests a non-survivable TBI?","CBV < 2 mL/100g")
B.YT=new A.c("What clinical parameter is estimated by the Pressure Reactivity Index (PRx)?","Cerebral autoregulation")
B.PI=new A.c("Recent studies suggest that the optimal Cerebral Perfusion Pressure (CPP) in TBI survivors with preserved autoregulation is approximately _____.","77.5 mmHg")
B.Yb=new A.c("What portable imaging technique can correlate with CT at a coefficient of 0.88 for measuring midline shift?","Transcranial color-coded duplex sonography (TCCDS)")
B.T3=new A.c("Which TCD-derived metric is used to correlate non-invasively with intracranial pressure (ICP)?","Pulsatility index")
B.Ol=new A.c("Approximately what percentage of patients lack an adequate temporal bone window for transcranial ultrasound?","10-15%")
B.S6=new A.c("Which portable CT scanner is commonly used for bedside neuroimaging in mobile stroke units?","CereTom (Samsung/NeuroLogica)")
B.NH=new A.c("What is the strongest prognostic CT marker for functional outcome in modern scoring systems?","Traumatic subarachnoid hemorrhage (tSAH)")
B.Qz=new A.c("What biological mechanism is believed to be the primary mediator of secondary injury detected by hippocampal QSM?","Iron-mediated oxidative stress")
B.Zx=new A.c("The Stockholm system is the only major CT score that includes which specific lesion type?","Diffuse Axonal Injury (DAI)")
B.N7=new A.c("In the Helsinki CT Score, what mass lesion size is the cutoff for increasing the score?","> 25 mL")
B.Yv=new A.c("According to the ACT-TBI study, what combination of CTP findings in the brainstem has high PPV for in-hospital mortality?","Matched decrease of CBF and CBV")
B.Zt=new A.c("What is the primary role of Foundation Model AI like Aidoc CARE in neuroimaging?","Multi-condition triage and automated ICH detection")
B.Xd=new A.c("True or False: Tau PET can reliably differentiate between all stages of CTE.","False (it may only detect high-stage CTE and has off-target binding issues)")
B.U2=new A.c("Which DTI metric specifically measures the extracellular water content to distinguish it from tissue integrity?","Free Water Volume Fraction (FW-VF)")
