B.UI=new A.c("According to updated 2021 data, what is the annual number of TBI-related deaths in the US?","69,000+ (approximately 190 per day)")
B.X8=new A.c("What has replaced motor vehicle crashes as the leading cause of TBI-related death in the US?","Firearms (primarily suicide)")
B.P9=new A.c("Which age group has the highest incidence of TBI related to motor vehicle crashes and sports?","15-24 years")
B.Uy=new A.c("What is the leading cause of TBI-related death in children aged 0-4 years?","Assault")
B.VG=new A.c("What is the approximate Male:Female ratio for Traumatic Brain Injury?","3:2")
B.ZI=new A.c("By what percentage is mortality estimated to decrease if severe TBI management guidelines are followed?","50%")
B.Qo=new A.c("What is the Glasgow Coma Scale (GCS) range for a Moderate TBI?","9-12")
B.a_5=new A.c("A patient with a loss of consciousness (LOC) of 15 minutes and a GCS of 14 is classified as having a _____ TBI.","Mild")
B.Wb=new A.c("What is the minimum duration of Post-traumatic Amnesia (PTA) required to classify a TBI as 'Severe'?","Greater than 7 days")
B.Tp=new A.c("What is the maximum duration of loss of consciousness (LOC) allowed for a diagnosis of Mild TBI?","30 minutes")
B.Qw=new A.c("Which TBI severity parameter is defined as the strongest single predictor of functional outcome?","Post-traumatic Amnesia (PTA)")
B.Qc=new A.c("Define: Contrecoup injury","Brain damage occurring on the opposite side of the impact site.")
B.VF=new A.c("In blast injuries, what is the 'Primary' mechanism of injury?","The blast wave or overpressure.")
B.Pk=new A.c("Which type of head injury carries the highest risk for post-traumatic seizures (33-50%)?","Penetrating injury")
B.Nm=new A.c("What is the recommended target range for Cerebral Perfusion Pressure (CPP)?","60-70 mmHg (CPP = MAP - ICP)")
