B.Ve=new A.c("What is the updated pooled prevalence of any pituitary axis dysfunction post-traumatic brain injury according to the 2024 meta-analysis?","33%")
B.Yl=new A.c("Why is the hypothalamic-pituitary axis uniquely vulnerable to damage during TBI?","Its location within the rigid sella turcica and dependence on the vulnerable hypophyseal portal vascular supply.")
B.Pg=new A.c("According to 2024 data, what is the prevalence of hypopituitarism in the first 3 months following TBI?","40%")
