B.VB=new A.c("Which emerging biomarker differentiates central DI from primary polydipsia with high accuracy?","Copeptin.")
B.OU=new A.c("In the Triphasic Response of DI, what characterizes Phase 2?","An SIADH-like phase of hyponatremia due to uncontrolled ADH release from dying neurons.")
B.Se=new A.c("In the Triphasic Response of DI, why must DDAVP be stopped if the patient enters Phase 2?","Continuing DDAVP during the antidiuretic phase causes severe water intoxication and hyponatremia.")
B.Pt=new A.c("Permanent Diabetes Insipidus occurs when more than _____% of ADH-producing neurons are destroyed.","80%")
B.TF=new A.c("Which pituitary deficiency is considered the most dangerous to miss because it can lead to fatal refractory hypotension?","ACTH deficiency (Secondary Adrenal Insufficiency).")
