B.agY=new A.O("According to the Lance definition (1980), what is the defining characteristic of spasticity that distinguishes it from other forms of hypertonia?",B.a5j,0,"The hallmark of spasticity is that the resistance felt during a passive stretch increases as the speed of the movement increases.","spasticity-motor")
B.a4j=s(["The hypertonia is primarily dynamic and likely to respond to chemodenervation.","The joint has a fixed contracture that requires surgical intervention.","The resistance is velocity-independent and suggests a basal ganglia lesion.","The patient has fatigable clonus lasting less than 10 seconds."],t.s)
B.ahD=new A.O("A clinician calculates the dynamic component of spasticity using the Modified Tardieu Scale. What does a large R2 - R1 value indicate?",B.a4j,0,"A large difference between the catch angle and full range of motion indicates a significant dynamic spastic component.","spasticity-motor")
