B.a3x=s(["It has a high risk of causing fatal hepatotoxicity.","It can negatively impact cognitive recovery and new learning.","It acts peripherally and causes too much generalized weakness.","It requires frequent blood draws to monitor therapeutic levels."],t.s)
B.afX=new A.O("Why is Diazepam generally avoided in the management of spasticity during the acute recovery phase of TBI?",B.a3x,1,"Benzodiazepines cause sedation and can impede the neuroplasticity and cognitive processing necessary for rehabilitation.","spasticity-motor")
