B.ahE=new A.O("Before initiating pharmacotherapy for a newly agitated patient, what is the single most important clinical principle to follow?",B.a8G,1,"Identifying treatable triggers like occult fractures or UTIs is the absolute first step in management.","agitation-behavioral")
