B.a6P=s(["To prevent evening insomnia","To match the peak risk of seizures","To allow for renal clearance by nighttime","To avoid interaction with evening beta-blockers"],t.s)
B.ahW=new A.O("When administering Amantadine for the dual benefit of reducing agitation and promoting cognitive recovery, why is the second dose usually given by noon?",B.a6P,0,"Amantadine's dopaminergic effects can be stimulating, making it difficult for patients to sleep if given late.","agitation-behavioral")
