B.a7I=s(["Up to 60%","Less than 10%","Approximately 25%","90%"],t.s)
B.agM=new A.O("According to the sources, what is the prevalence of pre-injury substance use disorders (SUD) among TBI patients requiring inpatient rehabilitation?",B.a7I,0,"A majority of patients requiring rehabilitation have a history of substance use, which is a significant risk factor for injury.","agitation-behavioral")
