B.a7w=s(["It leads to immediate midline shift and rapid deterioration","It results in a slowly expanding hematoma without obvious early clinical symptoms","It causes the hematoma to be limited by cranial suture lines","It prevents the formation of a crescent shape on imaging"],t.s)
