B.afF=new A.O("Nutrition is critical in TBI management. What is the recommended protein intake for a TBI patient during the hypermetabolic phase?",B.a9K,2,"TBI induces a state of significant hypermetabolism (140% baseline caloric expenditure), necessitating higher protein intake of 1.5-2.0 g/kg/day.","tbi-fundamentals")
